headline.main: China to Take Further Steps to Support Private Investment: State Planner
headline.print_headline: China to Take Further Steps to Support Private Investment: State Planner

lead_paragraph: China will take further steps to support private investment, Zhong Yong, a vice chairman of the state planner, said on Monday.
